{
  "stem": "6719.9",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, where?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the Army?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the Navy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the Air Force?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, but where did he serve?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said, in the SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said, look, I'll make a deal with you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said, you tell your dad to come down to Toronto, and I'll pay his expenses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'll pay for his gas, and I'm going to invite him for lunch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And if he can't do that, I said, I'll go down there and sit down there with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He says, my father wouldn't talk to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said, because you're a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then you hear this 'ah.' And I felt sorry for that kid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then he came to apologize for what he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And  I said, you don't have to apologize.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I said, but it points out what I told you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I said, somebody comes up to you and tells you that this guy that is next you is black, green, blue, or yellow, and therefore, since you are white, he's inferior.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And therefore, you can kill him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You can rob him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And if you do that, are you any different than the Nazis were?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the only incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the rest-- they-- first, you have to get on their level.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to talk their language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have to-- since you tell them how old you are, or they guess how old you are, you have to make them believe that you're still with it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you're one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tell them stories in the beginning about my granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, you know, everything that you got through, my granddaughter got through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, I deal with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I have to deal with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
